          <div align="center"> 
           <p>Back on the main world map screen, you can also open a jumbo-sized map by pressing the<br> "See Large Screen View" button:<br> </p> 
          </div></td> 
        </tr> 
        <tr align="center" valign="bottom"> 
         <td><a href="http://www.iris.edu/seismon/bigmap/index.phtml"><img src="largeViewButton.jpg" width="224" height="204" border="0" align="middle"><img src="../imgs/jumboMonitor.gif" width="304" height="163" border="0" align="middle"></a></td> 
        </tr> 
        <tr> 
         <td>
          <div align="center">
           The jumbo map has no interactive capabilities. 
           <br> It is meant for unattended display on a larger monitor in browser full-screen mode.
          </div></td> 
